In order to pass this module/set we need to follow instructionsgiven in it.

create a apex xclass named as AccountHandler, then add the followiing code.

public class AccountHandler {
    public static Account insertNewAccount(String name) {
        Account a =new Account();
        a.name = name;
        
        try {
            insert a;
            return a;
        }
        catch(Exception e) {
            System.debug('Error:' + e);
            return null;
        }            
    }

}
// now press ctrl +s to save the written code
in debug >> open execute anonymous window enter the following code:-

AccountHandler.insertNewAccount('');


